text: Cameraria diplodura is a moth of the family Gracillariidae. It was described by Bai in 2015.Global Taxonomic Database of Gracillariidae (Lepidoptera) It is found in China.Three new species, two newly recorded species and one newly recorded genus of Lithocolletinae (Lepidoptera: Gracillariidae) from China ==References== Category:Cameraria (moth) Category:Moths described in 2015
title: Cameraria diplodura
